law.text:
The STS Task Force shall be charged with:


Monitoring the effectiveness of paratransit software utilized for the provision of STS services;



Monitoring service provided by STS brokers and service providers;



Considering any other matters relating to the provision of STS services; and



Providing semiannual reports to the Board of County Commissioners regarding the effectiveness of paratransit software, the service provided by STS brokers and service providers and any other matters relating to the provision of STS services.
